All Python files **must** use snake_case for their file names.

✔ Use only lowercase letters, numbers and dashes (e.g. `run_main.py`, `auth_form.py`).
✖ Do NOT use camelCase, PascalCase, or underscores (e.g. `RunsTable.py` or `auth_Form.py`).
